name: Ink Wireframe
description:
Ink Wireframe plugin lets you create lo-fi wireframes.


With Ink Wireframe you can quickly drag and drop components and brainstorm your design ideas. Ink Wireframe plugin has 670+ unique variants for rapid prototyping. 


Ink Wireframe is an intuitive plugin with a zero learning curve for both designers and project managers. Ink Wireframe helps to prototype user flow and iterate quickly.


Ink Wireframe speeds up the design and iteration process. Ink Wireframe is ideal for shipping large-scale projects faster. Plugin lets designers to test ideas early on reducing scope of error.


Focus on your ideation and what really matters, rest Ink Wireframe will handle.
